org.sbfc.converter.sbml2sbgnml

Class SBML2SBGNML

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sbfc.converter.GeneralConverter
      • org.sbfc.converter.sbml2sbgnml.SBML2SBGNML

  • public class SBML2SBGNML
extends GeneralConverter
    Enable to convert a SBML model into SBGN-ML format. The layout part is not taken into consideration. This program use libSBGN milestone 1. libSBGN http://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/libsbgn/index.php?title=Main_Page SBGN-ML http://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/libsbgn/index.php?title=Exchange_Format
    Author:
    jalowcki

      • main

        public static void main(String[] args)
                 throws FileNotFoundException,
                        SAXException,
                        IOException
        Using jSBML, the given SBML file is read and loaded into objects. Then using libSBGN, the entire SBGN structure is built and a Sbgn object is created. This object will enable the final conversion into a SBGN-ML file.
        Parameters:
        the - SBML filename
        Throws:
        IOException
        SAXException
